Trade/Device Name(s): Audit® MicroControls™ Linearity FD Unsaturated Iron Binding Capacity
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Audit® MicroControls™ Linearity FD Unsaturated Iron Binding Capacity assayed quality control material simulating human serum for clinical chemistry linearity and calibration verification
Indications for Use Summary: Intended to simulate human patient samples for use in determining linearity, calibration verification, and verification of reportable range for unsaturated iron binding capacity in in vitro diagnostics
